result.name: Chung Kee Dessert - Flagship

reviews.text:
Great mango pomelo sago. Soooo much sago. Pomelo and mango pieces were tasty and fresh. Huge bowl for $33.

Tong Yoon with peanut (gelatinous rice ball with black sesame filling) was also good but sorry, no pic. $15.

Place was clean and air conditioned. The waitress answered a couple of noob questions I had. Don't think there's an English menu but pick something from the picture menu and you'll be right!
Very popular Cantonese style dessert shop
Good desserts and friendly staff. The service is quick and they didn't mind we got one dessert to share. Very refreshing and light shaved ice.
Always good. Never disappoint me. Tho I only stick with 'summer'(fruits with ice cream) and 幻彩明珠

reviews.text: 雖然不及以前既水準， 但比其他分店好食也平宜。 現在款示很多， 當然不會每樣都好食， 要自行留意那些比較出名的糖水了。
？？唔明點解咁多人等位時塞住條行人路，叫唔該都唔會讓路給人過，不知時下青年人想點，糖水只不過是糖開水，的糖水。🔥😠
